A team where the adc and jg get along about as well as Deidara and Sasori did, the top laner has some innate urge to protect his crazy team for no other reason than because they seem to appreciate and need it.  The mid is perpetually confused as to how he ended up on this team, but not altogether unhappy as he can now observe some interesting figures up close.  The support accepts her role and kindly watches over her bickering carry and jg, ever thankful that mid can take care of himself and that top does all he can to help.  A rag-tag team of champs who have no business being on the same team, but they work well together.

